imdb.plot outline: #ObjectHealth is a campaign aimed to drawing attention to the major global health challenges facing the world today. #ObjectHealth consists of 15 short documentaries that will be broadcast on "Para Todos la 2" , a daily programme on the Spanish La 2 channel, complemented by 15 short articles, to be published daily in Planeta Futuro as well as on the Health is Global blog.
